#: src/gui/ui/gsc_info_window.glade:404
msgid ""
"Self-tests are built-in tests within the drive designed to recognize drive "
"fault conditions. All self-tests are safe to user data. The tests can be "
"performed during normal system operation, but will take longer to complete "
"if the drive is not idle."
msgstr ""
"内置自检是驱动器内设计的测试功能，用于识别驱动器故障状况。所有自检对于用户数"
"据来说均为安全。测试可在系统正常运行时执行，但若驱动器未处于闲置状态，则完成"
"时间将延长。"

