#: src/gui/ui/gsc_preferences_window.glade:391
msgid ""
"Semicolon-separated blacklist regular expression patterns for device search. "
"For example, to blacklist all \"/dev/sd*\" devices, use \"sd.{1}$\". Simply "
"listing them as \"sda;sdb\" will also work."
msgstr ""
"以分号分隔的设备搜索黑名单正则表达式模式。例如，要将所有“/dev/sd*”设备列入黑"
"名单，请使用“sd.{1}$”。仅将它们列为“sda;sdb”也是可行的。"

